{
  "texts": [
    "These responses are then graded by a stronger LLM (GPT-4o was used in our experiments) with humancrafted reference answers.",
    "The scores are then assigned to each turn of the response.",
    "As shown in Table 4, SeaLLMs-v3-7B-Chat outperforms all other models in multilingual instruction-following across Indonesian (id), Thai (th), and Vietnamese (vi).",
    "It achieves the highest average scores in both individual turns and overall averages for each language.",
    "Specifically, SeaLLMs-v3-7B-Chat surpasses the previous version, SeaLLMs-7B-v2.5, by a significant margin (6.31 vs 5.15) and outperforms the strongest baseline model Qwen2-7B-Instruct (6.31 vs 5.70)."
  ]
}